RootWrapper
public abstract class ResourceMessageHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements HTTPXSynActionMessageHandler, Node

An abstract synchronous message handler that allows to process requests on a resource tree structure. (For a sample implementation see MyResourceMessageHandler in package de.fhg.fokus.restac.resource.demo) Last changed: 01.06.07 by Anna Kress
